'''Grey wolves''' are [[aggressive]] [[monster]]s found south of [[Yanille]] and guarding the entrance to the [[Wilderness Agility Course]].

==Locations==
*[[Feldip Hills]]
*Outside the [[Wilderness Agility Course]]
*Near the [[Scorpion Pit]] (East side of high level [[Wilderness]])

